results.name: Product of sexagesimal digits of Fibonacci numbers in base-60 representation.
comment: a(n) is the product of the terms in the n-th row of table A261575.
Conjecture: a(n) = 0 for n > 3329 (empirically checked up to 36000).
link: Reinhard Zumkeller, Table of n, a(n) for n = 0..10000
